The paper proposes a neural network architecture for solving POMDPs with non-uniform system dynamics, which involves combining planning and model learning. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Robotics (cs.RO), Systems and Control (cs.SY), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Given that the paper focuses on neural network architectures and learning, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. However, since the paper also evaluates its approach on robot navigation benchmarks, cs.RO is also a likely sub-category. Finally, since the paper deals with system dynamics and control, cs.SY is a possible sub-category, while cs.NE is also relevant given the use of neural networks.
